Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.00,0:00:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.40,0:00:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我媳妇百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.52,0:00:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是正夫的媳妇麻本百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.21,0:00:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请多多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.27,0:00:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前些天我刚成功求婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.00,0:00:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就想着快点介绍给爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.45,0:00:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.37,0:00:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.91,0:00:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是正夫的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.22,0:00:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫桑江沙门次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.85,0:00:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙门次郎先生么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.38,0:00:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人如其名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.16,0:01:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是个好色的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.05,0:01:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.09,0:01:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厨房借我用一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.26,0:01:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子说她要亲自做饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.50,0:01:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.81,0:01:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扰到你了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.17,0:01:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事  没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.95,0:01:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说你要亲自下厨 我好期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.52,0:01:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请进 请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.17,0:01:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.27,0:01:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.27,0:01:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.37,0:02:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,義父 ～百合子～\NJUC-445
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.52,0:02:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻本百合子\N（水城奈绪饰演）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.25,0:02:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑江沙门次郎\N（小泽徹饰演）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.22,0:02:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑江正夫\N（中泽荣司饰演）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.20,0:04:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嫉妒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.83,0:04:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这样妄想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到极限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.17,0:04:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快要高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.77,0:04:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使只是看一眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.86,0:05:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请用茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.77,0:05:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.60,0:05:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然间这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.92,0:05:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.82,0:05:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还在想你俩过着什么样的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.95,0:05:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是我们向爸爸你说不好意思才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.40,0:05:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.67,0:05:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就是一家人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.61,0:05:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来太正点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.22,0:05:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么漂亮的脸蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.85,0:05:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想和她做爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.50,0:05:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.65,0:05:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让人垂涎欲滴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.62,0:05:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.72,0:05:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿点心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.60,0:05:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.67,0:05:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有更好玩的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.50,0:06:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我揉一下乳房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.50,0:06:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.09,0:06:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.27,0:06:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你开玩笑开过头了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.20,0:06:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么诱人的毛衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.18,0:06:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看胸部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.33,0:06:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是看看我就忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.15,0:06:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行 放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.62,0:06:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.13,0:06:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.15,0:06:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昏过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.35,0:06:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.56,0:07:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你昏过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.66,0:07:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不正合我意嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.52,0:07:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡姿也好帅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.46,0:07:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看一下乳房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.42,0:07:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.03,0:08:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是揉揉乳房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.07,0:08:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就想射精了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.00,0:08:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.70,0:08:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我掀开衣服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.06,0:12:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洞口好小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.55,0:12:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来就像处女一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.60,0:13:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好秀丽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.63,0:13:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.76,0:13:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 一览无余啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.72,0:13:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.76,0:14:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正夫也好幸福啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.87,0:14:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.85,0:14:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩弄肉穴的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.27,0:14:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他到底还是不懂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.65,0:14:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就让我这个做爸爸的来教你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.74,0:14:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢做爱的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.97,0:15:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插进去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.02,0:15:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.84,0:15:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西插进身体里面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.25,0:15:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是在做爱么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.40,0:15:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在做爱么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.44,0:15:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有粗东西插进身体里面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.47,0:15:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.02,0:15:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.78,0:15:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.76,0:16:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好粗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.70,0:16:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.66,0:16:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.57,0:16:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.22,0:16:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.48,0:16:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.37,0:16:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我太放肆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.50,0:16:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.35,0:16:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.20,0:16:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.02,0:16:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.22,0:16:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.92,0:16:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.77,0:16:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.40,0:16:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.47,0:17:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.28,0:17:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.05,0:17:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停下 好漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.87,0:17:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.77,0:17:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.80,0:17:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,声音很可爱哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.05,0:17:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.73,0:17:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的肉棒插进里面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.40,0:18:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在抽插的是哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.40,0:18:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.92,0:18:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.59,0:18:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插的是那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.75,0:18:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里指的是哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.36,0:18:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.76,0:18:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.13,0:18:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.10,0:19:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 不要插得那么深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.60,0:19:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.57,0:19:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.66,0:19:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看得见么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.95,0:19:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看得见插入的地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.05,0:19:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.13,0:19:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.57,0:19:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要插得那么深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.07,0:19:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.80,0:20:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么讨厌做爱么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.20,0:20:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.30,0:20:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不愿意和你这种下流的爸爸做爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.13,0:20:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.02,0:20:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.82,0:20:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以插
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.33,0:20:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子 刚才已经插进去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.83,0:20:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.85,0:21:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不要插得那么猛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.35,0:21:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.46,0:21:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.73,0:21:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被这么粗的肉棒抽插
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.57,0:21:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.89,0:21:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插得好深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.72,0:21:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的肉棒正在抽插
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.50,0:21:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子 正在抽插的是哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.63,0:21:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.12,0:21:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊啊 不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.81,0:21:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.17,0:21:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.22,0:22:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.30,0:22:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 停下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.37,0:22:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么不行了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.03,0:22:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.82,0:22:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好淫荡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.67,0:22:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不是因为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.47,0:22:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.18,0:22:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的（肉棒）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.87,0:22:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
