Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.92,0:23:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再说一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.05,0:23:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子的哪里？快说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.83,0:23:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.32,0:23:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子的
