Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.13,0:24:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好喜欢爸爸的粗肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.73,0:24:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.93,0:24:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.23,0:24:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高潮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.99,0:24:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.76,0:24:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高潮的是哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:01.72,0:25:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊肉穴高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.86,0:25:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉穴高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:30.42,0:25:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的粗肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:35.07,0:25:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你会是这样的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:53.21,0:25:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫出声了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:01.48,0:26:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:03.25,0:26:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又要高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:05.45,0:26:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:07.05,0:26:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 不行了 不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:12.50,0:26:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:22.76,0:26:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 肉穴高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:27.67,0:26:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:29.47,0:26:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 肉穴高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:54.40,0:26:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:57.12,0:26:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:03.13,0:27:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要射了哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:16.92,0:27:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要射在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:19.06,0:27:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:37.30,0:27:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:40.42,0:27:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:59.67,0:28:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了好多精液在肉穴里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:04.56,0:28:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:07.35,0:28:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湿漉漉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:10.70,0:28:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:17.05,0:28:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:21.25,0:28:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到爸爸这么好色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:32.47,0:28:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子漂亮的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:35.93,0:28:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还硬邦邦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:39.60,0:28:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:41.72,0:28:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还想做么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:46.80,0:28:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是说过只是今天么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:53.60,0:28:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:55.43,0:28:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:26.16,0:29:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害羞么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:32.92,0:29:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:40.83,0:29:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:43.35,0:29:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍不住了么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:56.45,0:29:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乳头这么硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:04.47,0:30:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:06.10,0:30:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你说的是哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:09.52,0:30:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:32.16,0:30:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得舒服么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:39.38,0:30:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个好像很爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:45.22,0:30:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腰一晃一晃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:04.52,0:31:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:10.37,0:31:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,张开腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:16.62,0:31:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:24.66,0:31:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么不行？请放过我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:34.36,0:31:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来好像很爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:45.63,0:31:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,张开腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:00.33,0:32:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 不能继续下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:03.40,0:32:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不行的\N不能再继续了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:07.23,0:32:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正没有其他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:12.40,0:32:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄了哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:14.32,0:32:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服的是哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:23.42,0:32:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高潮时要说高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:29.75,0:32:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么舒服么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:48.70,0:32:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你品尝下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:54.07,0:32:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:56.52,0:32:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有更厉害的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:13.85,0:33:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:26.55,0:33:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比刚才爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:39.97,0:33:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:42.87,0:33:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伸直腰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:54.77,0:33:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 舒服么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:58.20,0:34:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表情很棒哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:01.13,0:34:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:04.46,0:34:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:07.57,0:34:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以体验那种怪怪的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:11.80,0:34:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也弄弄这个乳头 也弄弄这个乳头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:16.12,0:34:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:28.47,0:34:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还想要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:35.00,0:34:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果刺激那里会怎么样呢\N不行 不要刺激那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:43.76,0:34:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿开手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:47.50,0:34:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想体验下么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:07.20,0:35:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:14.17,0:35:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也张开腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:26.95,0:35:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍不住了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:34.30,0:35:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高潮时要说高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:39.53,0:35:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:47.35,0:35:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:48.56,0:35:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高潮了... 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:57.33,0:35:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:10.34,0:36:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍不住了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:38.72,0:36:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子 快看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:41.10,0:36:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒又变得这么硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:45.40,0:36:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:50.36,0:36:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:52.63,0:36:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:54.62,0:36:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想要么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:04.90,0:37:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:22.32,0:37:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:24.27,0:37:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要不愿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:48.42,0:37:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 很好 很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:57.12,0:37:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:02.90,0:38:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比百合子的那里热吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:09.86,0:38:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:46.02,0:38:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:48.85,0:38:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的肉棒好大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:52.45,0:38:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是么 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:54.72,0:38:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:57.75,0:38:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:09.07,0:39:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:15.10,0:39:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以含到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:47.33,0:39:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子(*╹▽╹*)好可爱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:59.43,0:40:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:01.16,0:40:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续吹给我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:24.10,0:40:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:26.66,0:40:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:33.92,0:40:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:46.90,0:40:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:54.17,0:40:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天还没结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:05.77,0:41:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:19.22,0:41:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:24.07,0:41:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那差不多又该插进百合子的肉穴里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:43.70,0:41:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:52.69,0:41:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:18.56,0:42:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的肉棒好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:23.93,0:42:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插得嘎吱嘎吱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:31.36,0:42:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他都这个年纪了 却还这么猛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:37.00,0:42:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再这么下去的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:39.40,0:42:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再这么下去的话我会抑制不住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:02.50,0:43:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:10.60,0:43:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:35.30,0:43:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:41.10,0:43:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 肉棒把肉穴插得不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:49.04,0:43:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,张开腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:53.20,0:43:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,张开腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:56.90,0:43:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:00.04,0:44:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看见没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:04.36,0:44:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒正在抽插百合子的肉穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:18.07,0:44:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 继续插下去的话我会不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:35.33,0:44:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:46.16,0:44:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:01.30,0:45:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:05.56,0:45:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:07.65,0:45:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:11.35,0:45:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用力晃动腰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:26.60,0:45:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:30.80,0:45:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒插得好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:32.86,0:45:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:41.09,0:45:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:46.60,0:45:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:02.77,0:46:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:16.47,0:46:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抬起屁股
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:25.56,0:46:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 不要舔那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:38.73,0:46:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:42.10,0:46:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插了哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:01.55,0:47:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不行了\N啊 高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:04.40,0:47:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 高潮了 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:14.62,0:47:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:22.10,0:47:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:30.95,0:47:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉穴高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:50.00,0:47:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做爱对象竟然是淫荡的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:53.20,0:47:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我尽然被他干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:06.20,0:48:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:07.97,0:48:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抬起腰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:07.92,0:49:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:11.32,0:49:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的精液的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:29.52,0:50:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:31.10,0:50:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该上班了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:33.45,0:50:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你为什么这么早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:37.10,0:50:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我难以忘记前几天百合子做的饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:42.09,0:50:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这周还会过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:46.90,0:50:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:48.37,0:50:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子 那就再做一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:51.50,0:50:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:53.60,0:50:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:01.57,0:51:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正夫不在时 我来你们这
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:03.20,0:51:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:05.05,0:51:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很为难吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:08.27,0:51:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:09.80,0:51:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天你对我做那种事\N你就不应该过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:13.56,0:51:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还清楚记得前几天的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:18.37,0:51:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你对正夫那样笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:21.80,0:51:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:24.26,0:51:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你欲求不满吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:28.36,0:51:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:34.50,0:51:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与那相比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:36.27,0:51:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续做昨天做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:40.20,0:51:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也太..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:41.77,0:51:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是约定好了只是昨天做的么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:44.45,0:51:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还没满足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:50.50,0:51:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要 停下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:54.25,0:51:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:06.00,0:52:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:15.45,0:52:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 停下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:20.25,0:52:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:22.91,0:52:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也太...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:23.96,0:52:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:26.17,0:52:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要传播出去么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:28.60,0:52:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是我的朋友还是正夫的朋友\N应该会很高兴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:51.20,0:52:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:53.75,0:52:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合子
